---
// WorkflowSection — code panel + terminal panel
---

<section class="workflow">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label reveal">How it works</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Write the contract. Verify the change.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub reveal">
      Criteria, evidence, and tracked files become machine-checkable edges.
      Supersigil shows where coverage comes from and when code changes put a
      spec back in question.
    </p>

    <div class="workflow-panels">
      <!-- Code editor panel -->
      <div class="panel reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 0.1s">
        <div class="panel-bar">
          <div class="panel-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
          <span class="panel-title">auth/req/login.mdx</span>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body code-panel">
          <pre><code><span class="c-gray">---</span>
<span class="c-teal">supersigil</span><span class="c-gray">:</span>
  <span class="c-teal">id</span><span class="c-gray">:</span> <span class="c-text">auth/req/login</span>
  <span class="c-teal">type</span><span class="c-gray">:</span> <span class="c-text">requirement</span>
  <span class="c-teal">status</span><span class="c-gray">:</span> <span class="c-text">approved</span>
<span class="c-gray">---</span>

<span class="c-muted"># User Authentication</span>

<span class="c-gold">&lt;AcceptanceCriteria&gt;</span>
  <span class="c-gold">&lt;Criterion</span> <span class="c-teal">id</span>=<span class="c-str">"valid-creds"</span><span class="c-gold">&gt;</span>
    WHEN a user submits valid credentials
    THE SYSTEM SHALL issue a session token
    within 200ms
    <span class="c-gold">&lt;VerifiedBy</span> <span class="c-teal">strategy</span>=<span class="c-str">"tag"</span> <span class="c-teal">tag</span>=<span class="c-str">"auth:valid-creds"</span> <span class="c-gold">/&gt;</span>
  <span class="c-gold">&lt;/Criterion&gt;</span>

  <span class="c-gold">&lt;Criterion</span> <span class="c-teal">id</span>=<span class="c-str">"invalid-creds"</span><span class="c-gold">&gt;</span>
    WHEN a user submits invalid credentials
    THE SYSTEM SHALL return a 401 response
    with a generic error message
    <span class="c-gold">&lt;VerifiedBy</span> <span class="c-teal">strategy</span>=<span class="c-str">"tag"</span> <span class="c-teal">tag</span>=<span class="c-str">"auth:invalid-creds"</span> <span class="c-gold">/&gt;</span>
  <span class="c-gold">&lt;/Criterion&gt;</span>
<span class="c-gold">&lt;/AcceptanceCriteria&gt;</span>

<span class="c-gold">&lt;TrackedFiles</span> <span class="c-teal">paths</span>=<span class="c-str">"src/auth/**/*.rs, tests/auth/**/*.rs"</span> <span class="c-gold">/&gt;</span></code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Terminal panel -->
      <div class="panel reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 0.2s">
        <div class="panel-bar">
          <div class="panel-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
          <span class="panel-title">Terminal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body term-panel">
          <pre><code><span class="c-muted">$</span> <span class="c-text">supersigil verify</span>

<span class="c-teal">auth/req/login</span>
  <span class="c-red"><b>&#10006;</b></span> <span class="c-muted">[missing_verification_evidence]</span> Criterion "invalid-creds": no matching evidence
  <span class="c-gold"><b>&#9888;</b></span> <span class="c-muted">[tracked_file_changed]</span> tracked file changed: src/auth/session.rs

<span class="c-red"><b>1</b></span> error(s), <span class="c-gold"><b>1</b></span> warning(s), 0 info(s) across <b>3</b> documents
<span class="c-muted">hint: Run `supersigil refs` to list criterion refs you can copy into evidence.</span></code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .workflow {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .workflow-panels {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
</style>
